<tr><td bgcolor="#363636">
<a name="bladestorm_katana_of_steel_sleet"></a>
<font color="#FFFFFF" face="Arial">
<strong>BladeStorm, Katana of Steel Sleet</strong>
<font size=-1></font><BR>
Skill: <a href="/weapons/2h_slash.shtml">2H Slash</a><BR>
Damage per second - 13.56<BR>
Damage 30 - Delay 45<BR>
Weight: 2.0 - All Races<BR>
Classes: <a href="/warrior/weapons/2h_slash.shtml">WAR</a><BR>
Effect: <a href="http://www.maximumeq.com/spells/individual/rain_of_swords.shtml?spellID=206">Rain of Swords</a><BR>
<font color=red>
(Magic) (No Drop) (Lore) <BR>
</font>
Dropped in Planeof Fear by Cazic Thule.Rain of Swords is a 950+ damage AE spell based on rain.<BR>

